fields.title: Amazing rallies!
fields.text: This rallies are insane! I thought I was getting better, but I have a long way to go!

fields.title: The Slammer Rip Off
fields.text: I hate this! Another company trying to become spikeball! The quality of their nets are rubbish! DO NOT BUY!

fields.title: Weekend fun!
fields.text: Checkout this awesome photo i captured at the weekend! It was some rally!

fields.title: Spikebouy!
fields.text: I bought this floating adaption for spikeball sets and it arrived this week! Planning to use it this weekend in the pool with my friends. I hope its as good as it looks!

fields.title: Spikeball Explained
fields.text: Found this great explanatory video for new players. Its such a fun game and so easy to learn! Have a go!
